HI!
This is the unfinished code to my Bachelor Thesis project, it comprises:
- A scraper to download news from Catalan news portal 3cat
- Some instructions to create a thematic parallel corpus to the news using AI
- A Spacy pipeline to annotate the data in UD 
- A small library to search for morphosyntactic features in the corpus, including examples
 :) A
 
